ient to you:\r\n\r\n<strong>If you\'re in Australia :</strong>\r\n\r\n9:00 to 11:00  AM French time = 7:00 to 9:00 PM in Sydney.\r\n\r\n<strong>If you\'re in Asia:</strong>\r\n\r\n11:00 AM to 13:30 PM French time= 7:00 to 9:30 PM in Tokyo or Seoul and 6:00 to 8:30 PM in Hong-kong and Beijing.\r\n\r\n<strong>If you\'re in the USA:</strong>\r\n\r\nthe best option is to book a lesson in the morning or during your lunch break: 5:00 PM to 7:00 PM French time= 11:00 AM to 1:00 PM in New-york  and 8:00 AM to 10:30 AM in Los- Angeles.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>For further details</strong> I suggest you use <a href=\"http://24timezones.com/\">This tool</a>  that will help you make the conversion to your timezone.','Buy/book your session(s)','','inherit','open','open','','184-revision-v1','','','2014-11-25 18:59:54','2014-11-25 17:59:54','',184,'http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/184-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(281,1,'2014-11-25 19:00:19','2014-11-25 18:00:19','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/eiffel-tower-paris-france-autumn.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-139\" src=\"http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/eiffel-tower-paris-france-autumn-300x168.jpg\" alt=\"eiffel-tower-paris-france-autumn\" width=\"473\" height=\"265\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAre you thinking of going to France or any other French-speaking country either for business or for leisure? Do you want to improve your French language skills at an affordable price? Look no further! My reliable and cost effective French tutoring services can certainly make it easier for you to learn the language without hassles and stress.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a style=\"color: #000000;\" title=\"Iconeo\" href=\"http://www.iconeo.fr\" target=\"_blank\">Lien</a></span>\r\n\r\nFrench is spoken by more than hundred millions of native speakers, has one-hundred ninety millions non-native speakers all over 