naughey and Naomi Watts. In Aokigahara,  Japan,  there is a mysterious forest known as The Sea of Trees. This is where locals go to contemplate life and death. Arthur, a suicidal American traveller ventures to this place  only to meet Takumi Nakamura who got lost in the forest. This woman will change Arthur\'s outlook on life and together they will fight to survive the forest. Van Sant has already won a Palme d\'or, in 2003, for the movie Elephant...\r\n\r\n<strong>The Valley of Love</strong> is a French movie by <span class=\"st\">Guillaume Nicloux</span>. The action takes place in the Californian Death Valley which is presented as a mysterious and maybe even supernatural  place. A former couple, played by Isabelle Huppert and Gerard Depardieu receive an invitation to the Death Valley. the only problem is that the  invitation comes from their son who has committed suicide 6 months ago.\r\n\r\nHere is the French trailer:\r\n\r\n[embed]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ca6aRd9uypw[/embed]\r\n\r\nWith so many interesting films, the Cannes Film Festival 2015 is bound to uphold the name and reputation that the past festivals have built up. Out of the films in the competition which ones would you to see?\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','The Cannes International Film Festival 2015','','inherit','open','open','','487-revision-v1','','','2015-05-11 20:21:32','2015-05-11 18:21:32','',487,'http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/blog/2015/05/11/487-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(502,1,'2015-05-13 17:17:47','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Brouillon auto','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-05-13 17:17:47','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/?p=502',0,'post','',0),(503,1,'2015-05-16 01:53:31','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Brouillon auto','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-05-16 01:53:31','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/?page_id=503',0,'page','',0),(504,1,'2015-05-16 02:09:41','0000-00-00 00:00:00','&nbsp;\n<h1>          